      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "These capabilities make it a strong choice for teams already using JavaScript stacks, as it minimizes the need for complex preprocessing or custom model training. The API's consistency across environments ensures reliable behavior in both server-side and client-side code."
