      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For large images, consider resizing or compressing them before sending to reduce latency and avoid API limits. The API has a maximum file size of 10MB, so preprocess images using libraries like sharp in Node.js. Additionally, implement retry logic for transient errors, such as network timeouts or rate limits."
          }
