          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Cost Analysis and Scaling Considerations"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Nanonets charges per API call, with pricing starting at $5 per 1,000 requests for the OCR S model. Volume discounts are available for high-traffic applications, making it cost-effective at scale. However, monitor usage closely to avoid unexpected bills, especially during development or testing phases."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To optimize costs, consider:"
